这一部分展示了规划导师与你沟通交流以后为你制定的申请意向专业方向、申请国家、申请形象、学术主线、个人特色副线。申请形象指的是你的申请材料希望给招生官展现你是怎样一个人，在一些可量化可直接对比的成绩成就奖项等硬件之外，还能体现你怎样的个性、品质、故事、特点、兴趣和热情，往往这些软性的东西更能让招生官对你印象深刻。学术主线是申请意向专业方向的展开和细化，个人特色副线则是在学术主线之外你的第二主要特点，有可能是另一个有一定联系或一定反差的学术线，也有可能是非学术的例如户外冒险、艺术音乐、某种理念追求、某个方面的社会关怀等等。学术主线和个人特色副线共同塑造一个更为立体、更为多元、更有区分度的申请形象，使你从同专业方向的申请者中脱颖而出。

Michael is applying to study Mathematics at top U.S. universities because his academic and extracurricular record already demonstr ates a rare depth of talent in the field. Through years of rigorous training in the AMC → AIME → USAMO →MOP pipeline, and with dis tinctions such as repeated invitations to MOP and international contest recognition (e.g., RMM medal), Michael has proven that he th rives in high-level mathematical problem solving. Choosing mathematics as his majoor is a natural continuation of this trajectory, allo wing him to deepen his theoretical foundation while opening doors to research in pure and or applied mathematics at the highest a cademic level.

Michael's application will present him as a top-tier Olympiad mathematician with sustained research potential. His profile combin es elite competition credentials (MOP, RMM, PRIMES-USA) with evidence of academic maturity and curiosity through research progra ms (tentative: Simons, UCSB RMP, PROMYS, SUMaC). This dual narrative - Olympiad excellence and research readiness - positions him not just as a strong math student, but as a future contributor to the academic community. His image will be that of a discipline d, high-achieving,research-minded young mathematician, someone who can thrive in a rigorous math department and stand out in the highly competitive applicant pool of top-10 U.S. schools.
